Package: NethackLogfiles
Type: Package
Title: Read Nethack Logfiles
Version: 0.99-1
Date: 2025-01-07
Maintainer: Enrico Schumann <es@enricoschumann.net>
Authors@R: person(given = "Enrico", family = "Schumann",
                  role  = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "es@enricoschumann.net",
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7601-6576"))
Description: Read logfiles of the most-ancient game of 'Nethack'.
  The package provides functions for parsing logfiles and xlogfiles.
  Abbreviations in those files (such as character class and alignment)
  can be expanded.
